title: Sunday Special: The Truth About Alex Jones
description:
On this Sunday Special of Human Events Daily, Jack Posobiec sits down with the one and only Alex Jones, host of Infowars, to discuss a wide variety of topics. From George Floyd and Kanye West to the CCP and digital currency, Posobiec and Jones will keep you on the edge of your seat! Alex Jones shares his experiences in court and compares that to what’s currently happening with Darrell Brookes in Waukesha. Jack asks what role God and faith play in Jones’ life - the answer might shock you. This is one episode of Human Events Daily that you just can’t miss!



Here’s your Daily dose of Human Events with @JackPosobiec
